00:00:46.573 --> 00:00:46.834
You know,

00:00:46.874 --> 00:00:49.555
time kind of mellows to the point where

00:00:49.936 --> 00:00:51.777
it's difficult to know exactly where we

00:00:51.817 --> 00:00:53.098
are on the calendar as

00:00:54.261 --> 00:00:55.100
is beautiful.

00:00:55.801 --> 00:00:57.341
I hope you enjoy the scenes of the

00:00:57.481 --> 00:01:00.883
