00:03:29.200 --> 00:03:32.223
that God does not like, he didn't listen,

00:03:32.902 --> 00:03:34.264
he was not responsive,

00:03:34.924 --> 00:03:37.185
he didn't engage and work and made no

00:03:37.224 --> 00:03:38.765
contribution of any kind,

00:03:39.366 --> 00:03:42.987
and he proved himself to be unreliable as

00:03:43.027 --> 00:03:45.188
well as uninteresting.

00:03:45.209 --> 00:03:46.229
He had no character.

00:03:47.090 --> 00:03:49.510
Dode is the opposite of these things.

00:03:49.531 --> 00:03:50.891
Dode is the man who

00:03:52.717 --> 00:03:55.717
worked more diligently with Yahweh than

00:03:55.758 --> 00:03:56.158
any other.

00:03:56.538 --> 00:03:59.840
He is the man that not only drew

00:04:00.080 --> 00:04:01.800
Israel together as a nation,

00:04:01.841 --> 00:04:04.722
brought them into Jerusalem as the

00:04:04.762 --> 00:04:07.683
capital, acquired the Temple Mount,

00:04:08.063 --> 00:04:10.145
but successfully defended God's people.

00:04:10.564 --> 00:04:14.687
He wrote between Mismore and Mishal,

00:04:14.747 --> 00:04:16.908
Proverbs and Psalms, a hundred verses.

00:04:17.769 --> 00:04:21.872
He was prolific in terms of his study

00:04:22.452 --> 00:04:23.132
of the Torah,

00:04:23.653 --> 00:04:26.755
as well as his literature exclaiming it.

00:04:27.255 --> 00:04:30.338
And beyond this defense of Israel,

00:04:30.377 --> 00:04:31.877
the unification of Israel,

00:04:31.918 --> 00:04:35.000
the building the city of Dode and

00:04:35.019 --> 00:04:35.661
Jerusalem,

00:04:36.021 --> 00:04:38.562
acquiring the Temple Mount and writing

00:04:38.601 --> 00:04:43.204
